      <abstract abstract-type="toc">
        <p>In this month's editorial, the <italic>PLoS Medicine</italic> Editors call
                    for more attention to the practices and influence of the alcohol industry on
                    health research, government policy, and public perceptions.</p>
      </abstract>
      <counts>
        <page-count count="2"/>
      </counts>
